<title>CZECH REPUBLIC: Czech IPB takes Vertex control.</title>
<headline>Czech IPB takes Vertex control.</headline>
<dateline>PRAGUE 1996-08-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>The financial group connected to Investicni a Postovni Banka a.s. (IPB) said on Thursday that it had taken control of the Czech glass fibre producer Vertex a.s.</p>
<p>Spokesman for IPB investment arm Prvni Investicni, Tomas Kopriva, told Reuters that the IPB Group had placed its chosen directors on Vertex's board by controlling more than 51 percent of the voting shares present at an extraordinary shareholders meeting in the eastern Czech town of Litomysl.</p>
</text>
